## Book Management CRUD Application

This Node.js application provides a simple CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) interface for managing a book collection.

**Features**

- Add new books to your collection.
- View a list of all books.
- Search for specific books by title, author or id.
- Update existing book information.
- Delete books from your collection.

**Getting Started**

**Prerequisites:**

- Node.js (version 14 or later): [https://nodejs.org/en/download](https://nodejs.org/en/download)
- npm (Node Package Manager) comes bundled with Node.js.

**Installation**

1. Clone the Repository:
   git clone https://github.com/Syedlukhman/digitalPaani.git

2. Install Dependencies:
   cd <your-repo-name>
   npm install

3.Running the Application
Start the Server:
npm test

Access the Application:
Open your web browser and navigate to http://localhost:9000 to access the Book Management application.
